name: Diamond - Crocodile
description:
Crocodile - 9th of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection.
The crocodile Bujan Senan was once a man, the most courageous warrior named Simalungun, who was never defeated by anyone in a fair fight. However, his wife betrayed him to his enemies, who ambushed and killed him. The spirit of the warrior became a huge crocodile, which from now on began to haunt people on the Lupar River.
We immortalized his image in this art, so that he remains a legend.
----///----
1920 x 1920 px / 25 fps / Loop
